{"tid":465622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11 月 紐 約 氣 溫 跌 至 -3.3 ℃   破 最 凍 記 錄","createTime":"2017-11-11T17:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T19:07:43.000Z","uid":82845,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a06acc2a962b0fa8b0de6622fa300d8c08fc2c19","tid":465622,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171111/large/1510388796_83fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171111%2Flarge%2F1510388796_83fd.jpg&h=9ff1e5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171111/large/1510388798_bc1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171111%2Flarge%2F1510388798_bc1e.jpg&h=9c8bc6db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 踏入11月中旬，美國紐約市迎接第一股寒流，中央公園周五晚上氣溫只有-3.3℃，成為市內歷來最冷的11月10日。受寒流影響，當地街上行人明顯減少，大褸、毛衣、手套等禦寒衣物亦紛紛出動。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道，紐約周五的日間氣溫仍有1.7℃，但一到晚上就跌至-3.3℃，日夜溫差明顯。紐約曾於1914年11月10日錄得氣溫-2.77℃，因此今年已打破市內同日最低溫度記錄。<br />\n<br />\n美國國家氣象局周五晚發出寒冷天氣警告，警告將生效至周六早上8時。這股寒流估計周末就會退去。根據天氣報告，周六早上紐約氣溫雖仍只得-4.4℃，但下午有望回升至2.8℃至6℃，而下周更將進一步回升至10℃左右。<br />\n<br />\n中央社／美國全國廣播公司 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港熱撚到,D暖化撚又走左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9abee9c904110aebc24f208599b5f4b02240f03c","tid":465622,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"同日"},{"pid":"e3a2d21a288ad61771d85e38c70cf7cf8cc38735","tid":465622,"uid":30966,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"極端天氣"},{"pid":"8d68731dacb733df7f20778a828eefe9561cfc2b","tid":465622,"uid":132038,"like":14,"dislike":6,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:12:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cd379c08c14813dbd24e35dc27766741df70684","tid":465622,"uid":7840,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:15:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"390a4a7b28b01605ec296737883ec56ee086e3ce","tid":465622,"uid":33439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國果種乾凍其實唔算好凍<br />\n我地香港濕凍13、4同根本同外國零下負20度無分別</blockquote><br />\n咪係，香港濕凍全世界最凍"},{"pid":"f5fe9c4598d3ff6f4bdab1db44ed04a4ad2a782d","tid":465622,"uid":16818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:27:33.000Z","msg":"香港幾時凍啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90131541fc736191746caa4a390d258086895e89","tid":465622,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:08:10.000Z","msg":"香港熱撚到,D暖化撚又走左去邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f650ecff6d9007aaf60aef93d83c7b42cf8362","tid":465622,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:11:58.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d31d0c45bc2d5aa257b578d82c33f352b227c39","tid":465622,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港熱撚到,D暖化撚又走左去邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得香港先有暖化<br />\n呀 唔係 應該係極端天氣先岩<br />\n總之凍同熱都係氣溫唔正常<br />\n要全地球都保持係25.5度先正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ccb5c72a6db3f338a3813774318de9a6845db37","tid":465622,"uid":154264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:53:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"356b656b1ff1bb8beb4c5b7930ecf4c923fad473","tid":465622,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>濕凍撚：香港濕凍凍過紐約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b5eb2235e1cdd5d30a990843d8a4e1c42319f4","tid":465622,"uid":70808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頭先出街係幾凍, 不過都無著羽絨<br />\n香港啲人十五六度都著撚晒羽絨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33e942ad2b51c14b11606a7cd5ba0952cc0afb3","tid":465622,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:03:46.000Z","msg":"冬天凍過平均數=極端氣候<br />\n冬天暖過平均時=全球暖化<br />\n無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcef83461cb4ab5f03b513b617c187e7e358dcf","tid":465622,"uid":80176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實暖化會影響洋流<br />\n再影響地區溫度"}]}